  "id": "php/associativearrays",
  "contentHtml": "<h1>Associative Arrays</h1>\n<p>Use named keys that you assign.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-php\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;?php</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$foods</span> = [<span class=\"hljs-string\">'Pizza'</span>=><span class=\"hljs-string\">\"12\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">'Apple'</span>=><span class=\"hljs-string\">'16'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">'Banana'</span>=><span class=\"hljs-string\">'12'</span>];\r\n<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">var_dump</span>(<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$foods</span>);\r\n\r\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\">?></span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2>Access Associative Arrays</h2>\n<p>Refer to the key name.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Access array item.</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-php\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;?php</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$foods</span> = [<span class=\"hljs-string\">'Pizza'</span>=><span class=\"hljs-number\">12</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">'Apple'</span>=><span class=\"hljs-number\">16</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">'Banana'</span>=><span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>];\r\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">echo</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">$foods</span>[<span class=\"hljs-string\">'Apple'</span>];\r\n\r\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\">?></span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2>Change Value</h2>\n<p>Use key name.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-php\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;?php</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$foods</span> = [<span class=\"hljs-string\">'Apple'</span>=><span class=\"hljs-number\">12</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">'Banana'</span>=><span class=\"hljs-number\">6</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">'Squash'</span>=><span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>];\r\n<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$foods</span>[<span class=\"hljs-string\">'Squash'</span>] = <span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>;\r\n<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">var_dump</span>(<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$foods</span>);\r\n\r\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\">?></span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2>Looping Through an Associative Array</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-html\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;!DOCTYPE <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">html</span>></span>\r\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;<span class=\"hljs-name\">html</span>></span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;<span class=\"hljs-name\">body</span>></span>\r\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;?php\r\n    $foods = ['Apple'=>12, 'Banana'=>6, 'Tomato'=>7];\r\n    \r\n    foreach ($foods as $key=>$val) {\r\n        echo \"$key: $val &#x3C;br>\";\r\n    }\r\n?></span>\r\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">body</span>></span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">html</span>></span>\n</code></pre>",
